01:00:29,600 --> 01:00:33,700
Usput, trebao sam se naci s prijateljem.
Mislim da je kod vas odsjeo.

593
01:00:34,400 --> 01:00:38,000
Zove se Brian Speer. S-P-E-E-R.

594
01:00:41,900 --> 01:00:45,100
Oprostite, g. King, nemamo
nikoga pod tim imenom.

595
01:00:45,400 --> 01:00:46,800
